title: Senior Shoutouts: Cullman Soccer
text:
With the coronavirus outbreak canceling school, graduations and sports, WVTM 13 wants to give a special shout out to the seniors in Alabama! Check out the seniors on the Cullman High School soccer team in the video above.Have a senior class photo you want to share? Send them to wvtm13@wvtm.com! Check out the gallery below.
